<p>關東軍推動建立偽滿洲國。偽滿洲國設立異常辦公室。<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/the-song-of-mckao">異常辦公室隊歌誕生。</a></span></p>
